Detailed information at: http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Update

== Installation ==

To install this extension, add the following to LocalSettings.php:
require_once("$IP/extensions/Update/Update.php");
#add configuration parameters here

== Support ==

It's hoped that you will enjoy the extension, and if you do, consider purchasing it as a pay-what-you-want scheme on the author's website ( http://olivierbeaton.com/mediawiki#update ).
If you find a bug or wish to make a feature request, please contact the author by email olivier.beaton@gmail.com. The talk page is also monitored. The author is often in the #mediawiki irc channel under the nick Finlay.